note number-triangle.vrb — each row prints its row number repeated row times.
note Row 1: 1, Row 2: 2 2, Row 3: 3 3 3, etc.

ask the user "how many rows?" and save to rows.

row = 1.
while row <= rows:
    col = 1.
    while col <= row:
        display row.
        col += 1.
    end.
    say.
    row += 1.
end.
